---
<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-anthracite-900 via-anthracite-800 to-anthracite-900"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <img 
        src="/profile.png" 
        alt="Ralf Natale" 
        class="w-40 h-40 rounded-full mx-auto border-4 border-gold-500 shadow-2xl object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-4">
      <span class="text-white">Ralf</span> <span class="text-gold-500">Natale</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gold-400 font-light mb-6">
      IT-Consulting: Erfahren. Prozessorientiert. Effizient.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
      Über 20 Jahre Expertise in .NET-Entwicklung, Architektur und Beratung für Enterprise-Lösungen
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 bg-gold-500 text-anthracite-900 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gold-400 transition-colors shadow-lg">
        Kontakt aufnehmen
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#about" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-gold-500 text-gold-500 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gold-500/10 transition-colors">
        Mehr erfahren
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
